    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes an extension to the Open Shortest Path First (OSPF) protocol to allow a single physical link to be shared by multiple areas.  This is necessary to allow the link to be considered an intra-area link in multiple areas.  This would create an intra- area path in each of the corresponding areas sharing the same link. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
